Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,起床啦 新奥尔良 周一清晨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rise and shine, New Orleans. Monday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里呢 大概是堵在路上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where you at? Probably stuck in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,注意安全 多点耐心 因为我们都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So be careful today, be patient, because we all know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,某些司机比这交通拥堵更糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as bad as the gridlock is, some of the drivers are worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快报警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone call 911!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,本字幕仅作学习交流之用 禁止用于任何商业用途 否则后果自负
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FF00&}==GA字幕组=={\c}\N翻译：阿珂姑娘 羽林郎 岛酱 草菇 毯子 鱼香肉丝 剧中人 爱玺神的Cher·L\N校对：毯子 天羽流芳 秋秋  总校：毯子\N英文字幕：elder_man  时间轴调整：蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这车真漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a beaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚后 我给Linda买的第一辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First car I bought Linda after we got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一直停在车库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Been sitting in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,今早拖了过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had it towed over this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,出了什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 婚姻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you know, marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,本身就很困难 然后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hard enough as it is, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你不在家里住了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you're not living in the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说这辆车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You meant the car, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想知道这车出了什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to know what's wrong with the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我一直在你身边 King\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know I'm always here for you, King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎无法发动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Engine won't turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证我能修好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promised I'd get it fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-知道你在做什么吗 -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Know what you're doing?  - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,去试一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say when.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, give it a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识一个机修工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I got a mechanic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我姐的车别人都没辙 愣被他给修好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that fixed my sister's car when no one else could.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要他的号码么 -我能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You want his number? - I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,海军军官在法国区被发现身亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dead Navy officer in the Quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,车子驶离了马路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Car was run off the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-这车是怎么回事 -是Linda的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's with the car? - It's Linda's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,出了什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 King不在家里住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you know, King's not living at home anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,说车呢 Cristopher\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The car, Christopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她问的也是这辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She also means the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,据目击者称 今早9:30\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to witnesses, we've got two cars speeding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有两辆车沿康迪街狂飙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}down Conti at 9:30 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,轿车撞击了SUV\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sedan traded paint with an SUV,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,迫使其驶入了这个建筑工地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}forced it into this construction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,受害者死于撞击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Victim died on impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,路怒症么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what, road rage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,知道轿车的车牌号么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got plates on the sedan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,目击者称没有牌照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Witnesses say there weren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只见贴膜的车窗 黑色车身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just tinted windows, black car,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,保险杠有大凹陷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}big dent in the bumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,早 Loretta\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Morning, Loretta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,无论人的灵魂多么娴静温柔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter how quiet and gentle the soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们放在方向盘后 他们就会突然回归\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you get 'em behind a wheel and suddenly they revert
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原本的狰狞面目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the most base and primal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我坐过你的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. I've driven with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,根据驾驶员的驾照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. From the driver's license.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,死者是Darby Wilson中校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The deceased is Commander Darby Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在海军研究办公室（ONR）工作 本地人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Worked at the Office of Naval Research. Local guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在梅泰里出生长大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Born and raised in Metairie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以玩“猜死因"的游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could play Guess the Cause of Death,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这根巨大的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the giant rebar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,刺穿死者胸腔的螺纹钢筋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sticking through our victim's chest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,让这个游戏失去意义了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}makes the game kind of pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们迅速扑灭了火焰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They put out the flames fairly quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运的是 尸体基本无损\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luckily, the corpse is mostly intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do we got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,收据显示 是昨晚买的 晚上6:12\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Receipt says it was purchased last night. 6:12 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直不能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never understood the appeal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,珠宝的吸引力 又昂贵 又容易丢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of jewelry. Expensive, easy to lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,除了带在身上 没有任何用处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and doesn't do anything but just sit on your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,剩斗士如是说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Says the perennial bachelor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲有个盒式吊坠 里面装着我父亲去越南前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mother had a locket with my father's picture from...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在新兵训练营拍的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when he was in boot camp before Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,盒式吊坠的意义不在珠宝本身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The point of a locket isn't the jewelry itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而在于赠送者在里面放了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's what the giver chooses to put inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,待定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会发布那辆轿车的通缉令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll put a BOLO out on that sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看是否有监控摄像头拍摄到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See if any surveillance cameras get us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那个司机的长相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a better look at the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还有件事 Dwayne\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something else, Dwayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他光着脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got bare feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋子不在车上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His shoes are nowhere in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会不穿鞋就上车呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who gets in a car without shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,匆忙的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们假定 结局在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's assume that whatever ended here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,起始于另外某地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}started somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底打哪儿来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the hell was he coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有个GPS\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got a GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以开始干活了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...I can do my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,德尔加多大道 39163号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\i1}39163 Delgado Avenue.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson中校的房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\i1}Commander Wilson's house?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,和他驾照上的地址一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\i1}Matches the address{\i} {\i1}on his license.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 听听这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson今年四十岁 已经是中校了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilson was 40 years old, already made commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在伊拉克 阿富汗都执行过任务 获得无数嘉奖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tours in Iraq, Afghanistan. Numerous commendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而他竟然死于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he could be dead 'cause someone couldn't handle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-有人无法接受被插车 -嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- getting cut off in traffic. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,听我指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,海军罪案调查处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}NCIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chris\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看来跟路怒症没什么关系了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's not likely this has anything to do with road rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 背后还有更大的阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nope. Something much bigger going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,忙碌的清晨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Busy morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,关于受害者 还有什么消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got any more on our victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-第一位受害者 -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Our first victim? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,海军研究办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Wilson's assignment with the Office
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,派遣Wilson中校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Naval Research had him working
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,担任私人开发商的技术联络员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as a technical liaison for private developers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,特别权限 最高机密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Special access, top secret clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-把他的电脑带走 打电话给... -Patton Plame\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take his computer. Call in... - Patton Plame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让他进行分析\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get him to run a diagnostic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那第二位受害者呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And our second victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她是谁 Wilson中校的妻子么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's, what, Commander Wilson's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是否定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would be a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是Wilson中校的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Commander Wilson's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Katherine Wilson 而浴室里的裸女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Katherine Wilson. The naked woman in the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是Rebecca Ortega\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\i1}is Rebecca Ortega.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她是Wilson在ONR的助手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's Wilson's assistant at the ONR.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在厨房找到了她的包\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Found her purse in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一枪击中头部 一枪击中颈部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One gunshot to the head, one to the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,利落的射入伤 我猜是九毫米手枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clean entry wounds. My guess-- nine-millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,根据僵硬程度推测 9:00 9:15\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Based on rigor, 9:00, 9:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,距Wilson中校死于撞车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Less than 15 minutes before Commander Wilson dies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不到15分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一个助理早上九点在老板家洗澡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else finds it odd that an assistant is taking a bath
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有谁觉得这事很奇怪么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at her boss's house at 9:00 in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果中校的妻子知道这里发生的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if the commander's wife knew what was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道她会有什么反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}wonder how she'd react.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我还没忘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before I forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我说的那个机修工的号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's the number to the mechanic I told you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢 我自己来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, thanks. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 King 这家伙能让乌龟飞奔起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm telling you, King, this guy can get a turtle to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也告诉你 我能搞定 Christopher\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm telling you I got this, Christopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bart Roberts 他住在隔壁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bart Roberts. He lives next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跟Pride探员说说 Wilson中校和他妻子的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell Agent Pride here about Commander Wilson and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是一对爱吵架的夫妇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that was a couple that just loved to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bart说 Wilson的助理Rebecca\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bart says that Wilson's assistant Rebecca
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有几次在这里待到非常晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}spent some late nights here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有婚外情么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They in a relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I can't say that for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只能说...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but alls I will say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我的话 一定上了那个妞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would've tapped that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 上帝保佑她的灵魂之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, God rest her soul and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你今天愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a good day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 这是一段触礁的婚姻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, we've got a marriage on the rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,丈夫似乎有外遇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}husband seems to be having an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,心怀恨意的妻子枪杀了丈夫的情人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disgruntled wife shoots husband's lover
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把丈夫撞下马路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then runs him off the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,或者让别人来干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or gets someone else to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这个血迹了吗 是从鞋底脱落的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See this blood? It came off a shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我喷了些蓝星试剂 看这个尺寸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sprayed it with BlueStar. Look at the size.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很大 不是女人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big. Not a woman's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是中校的 他光着脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't from the commander. He was barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我在客厅里发现了更多血斑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found some more blood spots in the hall, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,和鞋印吻合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shoe prints match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 妻子雇凶杀人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, wife gets someone to do the deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他在浴室里射杀了Rebecca\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He shoots Rebecca in the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是中校跑掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the commander was able to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,逃出房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}flees the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,坏人追赶 中校上车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad guy follows, gets to the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,死于撞车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ends in a crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,先从妻子的私人资产查起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Start with the wife's personal assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看她是否有财力买凶杀人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See if she had the finances to pay someone to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,48小时前 Katherine Wilson的账户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}$20,000 withdrawn from Katherine Wilson's bank account
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,取出了2万美金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}48 hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,足够雇个枪手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough to get you a hired gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 King\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, King,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那些制服男是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who are the uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[路易斯安那]贝尔查斯的情报专家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Intelligence specialists out of Belle Chasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们总部刚开始翻修 我告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Revamp on their HQ just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,完工前他们可以用咱们后头的办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until it's done, I told them they could have offices in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说一句 从海军研究办公室那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the way, got a response
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了回复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the Office of Naval Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"考虑到中校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Given the access
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所拥有的权限 我们担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"the commander had, we are concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,敏感信息可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"about the sensitive information
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,从他的家用电脑里泄露"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that might have been taken off his home computer."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they're concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道他们担心的是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know who they're concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个去ONR\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two go to ONR.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我去跟那个2万美金的妻子谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll talk to the $20,000 wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们调查了我的银行记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You looked into my bank records?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可以解释一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mind explaining why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你上周为什么提取2万美金么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you withdrew $20,000 last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫死了 你却在盘问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My husband is dead, and you're questioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的财政状况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my finances?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须调查所有可能性 Wilson夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're required to cover our bases, Mrs. Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有杀我丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't kill my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有矛盾 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were having issues, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天在家里看到了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw him yesterday at the house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,商讨我们的离婚条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to go over the terms of our divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,起争议了么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it contentious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-没有别的么 -什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And nothing more? - Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,房子里的另一位受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other victim at the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,被杀害的那个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the woman who was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebecca 是的 我听说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rebecca. Yes, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她一清早就在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was there early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,助理和老板这时候在一起 很奇怪啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Odd time for an assistant to be with a boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And... there was this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在他的车里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,认识么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,知道是给谁的么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any idea who it was for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不是给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for me, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你要逮捕我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless you'd like to arrest me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我想我应该开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I should probably go start
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,安排我丈夫的葬礼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}planning my husband's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都十分震惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're... in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson中校和Rebecca\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Wilson and Rebecca were...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都是很棒的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}amazing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson中校在军中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Wilson had...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,前途光明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a bright future in the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,中校知道哪些敏感情报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of sensitive Intel was the commander privy to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,无人机 导弹防御\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drones, missile defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所有最新的技术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all the latest technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson中校出现过任何问题 或泄露过情报么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any issues there or breaches of intelligence with Commander Wilson?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很想具体谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'd love to talk specifics,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但那些信息是机密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that information's classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我们什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anything you could offer us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Darby和Rebecca去年和一个私人国防承包商\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darby and Rebecca spent much of the past year on-site
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,合作了很久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a private defense contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Axelrod工业公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, Axelrod Industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么问题 你应该跟他们谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there were issues, they'd be someone you should talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One other question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否感觉Wilson中校\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you get a sense that Commander Wilson
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,和Ortega女士有超出工作的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Ms. Ortega's relationship extended beyond work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 上将需要您签字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, excuse me. The admiral's requesting your signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Darby和Rebecca十分亲密 但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darby and Rebecca were close, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于我们严格的信息披露政策\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}given our strict disclosure policies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们如果恋爱 需要向我们汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they'd have to come to us with a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,或保持地下恋情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or keep it an office secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想万事皆有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要打包标记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to need to bag and tag
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,文件 平板电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the files, the tablet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,中校办公室的所有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}everything in the commander's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是NCIS的特别探员Brody\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Special Agent Brody with NCIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想 你是否想告诉我什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was wondering if there was something you might want to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I... I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,恰好那个时刻需要签字么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just needed a signature at that exact moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那么赶时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time-sensitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Darby和Rebecca之间没有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was nothing going on between Darby and Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我才是那个地下恋情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I'm the office secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你和Darby\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and Darby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我和Becca\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me and Becca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Darby和Becca十分亲密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darby and Becca were very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们工作到非常晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They worked crazy hours together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她有时候睡在他那儿 但是相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She slept there some nights, but trust me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebecca不喜欢他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...Rebecca wasn't into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我太痛苦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm in so much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们彼此相爱 而现在她...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, we were in love, and now she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对于您的损失 我非常抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以并没有婚外情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So there was no affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不代表他妻子也这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which doesn't mean the wife didn't think there was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对于那次取款 我想了解更多信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'd like to know more about that withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但我认为 这位女士不会凭直觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But she didn't strike me as the kind of lady that would...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就干掉两个人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bump off two people on a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 说起直觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, speaking of hunches--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道这意味着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I don't know what this means--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我在中校的右手腕上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I found a small patch of a sticky substance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了一小片黏性物质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the commander's right wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,测试过了么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Run any tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,用最传统的方式 嗅觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The old-fashioned kind: smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-烟草 -嗯 凝胶状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tobacco? - Mm-hmm. In resin form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is odd,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为中校有我见过的最干净的肺叶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because the commander has the cleanest lungs I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不禁使人好奇 它为什么出现在那儿 又来自哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Makes you wonder why is it there, and where exactly did it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sebastian正在进一步化验凝胶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sebastian's running further tests that resin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,以得到更多信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we could learn more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,说曹操...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}一种寻物游戏 通过说"冷""热"来表示方向是否正确 引导对方找到物件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,更热了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,更热了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这边比较冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咱这是干嘛呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,试图抵抗最高统治者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trying to beat back the prying eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,偷窥的目光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of our great overlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sebastian\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 这是我的反黑客程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry. It's my anti-hacking app.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人试图从我手机里窃取信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When someone tries to steal information from my phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这程序就会嘀嘀响 它在告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the app starts beeping, and it's telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,黑客源头就在这个房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the source of the hack is somewhere in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,更热了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,更热了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,焦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Singeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,炼狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,它显示来源在这具尸体里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's saying that the source is inside the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在尸体里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Uh, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right... there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我正好要检查胃容物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just about to check the contents of the stomach anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西嵌到了胃粘膜里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something's imbedded in the stomach lining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像是微芯片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like a microchip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以看一下么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I see that for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 哇哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 哇哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seriously, like, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过这种东西正在研发当中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I had heard this kind of thing was in development,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但亲眼看到一个... 哇哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but to actually see one... Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看到一个什么 Sebastian\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See one what, Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一个生物追踪器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, a biotracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种间谍工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a spy tool--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,用来植入另一个人的身体中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something that you put inside another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当那人靠近电脑或电话之类的电子信号时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then when that person is near an electronic signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个生物追踪器就会从信号中窃取信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like a computer or a phone, the biotracker steals that signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,窃听电话 拦截邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phone calls are tapped, e-mails are hijacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就像吞下了一个记录装置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like swallowing a recording device?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错 -所以你是说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. - So what you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson中校被人监视了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Wilson was being spied on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确是说Wilson中校被监视了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am saying that Commander Wilson was being spied on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,被自己体内的东西监视了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from inside his own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,生物追踪器是生物学和电子学的完美结合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Biotracker is the purest fusion of biology and electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有一系列技术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a whole branch of tech
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,用来制造这样的疯狂产品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}devoted to craziness just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说 这是当下最潮的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all the rage with guys like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一样的黑客们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hackers like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是计算机调查专家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Investigative computer specialists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是正当职业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too legit to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}有首歌叫<Too legit to quit> 演唱者是MC Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 MC Hamme\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, MC Hammer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么把生物追踪器植入人体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how do you get a biotracker into someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见 它们非常小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, as you can see, they're very tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,通常被藏在药片里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Normally, they're hidden in a pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有可能 是他自己吞下去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any chance he could have swallowed it himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 除非他疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not unless he's a crazy-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西没有经过检验 它们很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those things are not tested; they're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson中校在服用胆固醇药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Wilson was on cholesterol meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有人把生物追踪器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe somebody slipped the biotracker
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-藏在那里面了 -呃...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- into one of those? - Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能在多个药片里植入追踪器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they might have planted trackers in multiple pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像除芝士以外的所有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like anything other than...cheese,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,生物追踪器几天内就可以排出体外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}biotrackers can pass through your system within days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以生物追踪器窃取的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the info the biotracker steals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可以被发送到某个地方 你能追踪信息的下落么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can be transmitted somewhere-- can you track where it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不 超出我的超级能力范围了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah. That's beyond even my considerable powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this is not
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这不像是一个妒妇会用的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something a jealous wife would be using?
