Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:22:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好 待在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不明白怎么会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't get any of this.
