Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,导致他被杀害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was the reason for his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他有没有告诉过你什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anything he might have told you
