Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.34,0:24:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 夫人 我们会抓住凶手的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry, ma'am, we'll find the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Katherine 我需要你再好好回想一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Katherine, I need you to remember anything you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.06,0:24:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都发生得太快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, it just happened really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.59,0:24:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力想 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I'm trying. I...
