Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.87,0:24:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你最后一次见到你丈夫时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The last time you saw your husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.99,0:25:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他有没有说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}did he mention anything about meeting someone
