Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.91,0:25:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shang 他是个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shang. He's this... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.85,0:25:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有个人叫Shang\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone named Shang.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.91,0:25:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson说是个同事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14} He said he was a colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.94,0:25:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.64,0:25:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's good, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.58,0:25:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在通缉令中加上Shang\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Add Shang to the BOLO.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.06,0:25:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我和ONR谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll talk to ONR.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.61,0:25:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,交叉比对Wilson同事的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cross-reference the name against anyone Wilson worked with.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.47,0:25:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,两起谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Two murders
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.18,0:25:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有对Wilson夫人的谋杀未遂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and an attempt on Mrs. Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.55,0:25:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该把她送去安全屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's time maybe we move her to the safe house
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.89,0:25:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,直到把凶手绳之以法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}till the killer's in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.56,0:25:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我会安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.39,0:25:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让Brody帮她收拾行李\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have Brody pack her a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 King\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got it, King.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.42,0:25:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以后退几步吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mind taking a couple steps back?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.62,0:25:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,以防万一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.95,0:25:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候也有一个这样的收音机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used to have a radio like this growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:25:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,父母吵架时 我就把它开得超大声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turn it up real loud when my parents would argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.92,0:26:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈酗酒 爸爸大吵大嚷 音乐能让一切都好过些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom drank too much, Dad yelled and the music just made it easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.00,0:26:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.16,0:26:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢那首歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.28,0:26:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Darby不喜欢音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darby didn't like music.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.42,0:26:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他向来一本正经 直入正题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was no-nonsense. Always on point.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.60,0:26:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇见他时 很爱他这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which, when I met him, I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.05,0:26:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是相处久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But time passes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.24,0:26:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你当初爱上的那些不同点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the differences you fell in love with just...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.37,0:26:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就变成了隔阂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}oh, start to be differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.62,0:26:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你结婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.72,0:26:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.60,0:26:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白我的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.39,0:26:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 感情破裂时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, it's tough
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.84,0:26:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,日子很难熬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when things get broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.52,0:26:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿了么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.01,0:26:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,饿了 我好像几天都没吃东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I don't think I've eaten in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.33,0:26:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.42,0:27:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,花生酱 大米 烤豆子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}peanut butter, rice, baked beans
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.30,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一罐莎莎酱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a can of salsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.23,0:27:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你能用这些东西做顿饭出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can make a meal out of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.53,0:27:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你可不知道我的本事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know who you're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.23,0:27:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了 Brody\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Brody.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.93,0:27:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那些情报专家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The intelligence specialists--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.55,0:27:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿了我的土豆沙拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they took my potato salad,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.51,0:27:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都没问过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}didn't even ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.14,0:27:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,少来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.57,0:27:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你不吃土豆沙拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you don't eat potato salad,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.15,0:27:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我没吃 而King不在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't eat it, and King ain't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.29,0:27:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就只剩一种可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That leaves us one option.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.82,0:27:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中间出了贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got thieves in our midst.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.38,0:27:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们煮了咖啡 多体贴呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They made coffee. That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.10,0:27:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,随你怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.07,0:27:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.15,0:27:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是Shang Lee\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meet Shang Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.78,0:27:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson中校的同事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Wilson's colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.48,0:27:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilson在水烟坊里的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilson's friend from the hookah bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.22,0:27:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shang以前就职于Axelrod工业公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shang used to work at Axelrod Industries--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.38,0:27:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,技术官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}technology officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.00,0:27:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Axelrod先生说他一年前开除了Shang\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Axelrod says he fired Shang a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.58,0:27:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,控告他企图把蓝图卖给竞争对手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Accused him of trying to sell blueprints to a competitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.18,0:27:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个生物追踪器可能与此有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could be what the biotracker is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.69,0:27:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,试图了解Wilson在Axelrod公司的工作内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An attempt to learn what Wilson was working on
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.53,0:27:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样Shang就可以转售\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at Axelrod so Shang could resell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.71,0:27:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-也许被Wilson发现了... -所以Shang不得不灭口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe Wilson finds out... - Shang has to silence him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.93,0:27:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shang Lee现在在哪儿 -看起来是销声匿迹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's Shang Lee now? - Looks like he's in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.19,0:28:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会逮到他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.56,0:28:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,以及偷了我土豆沙拉的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And whoever stole my potato salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.19,0:28:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,存在着数十亿星系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are billions of galaxies out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.86,0:28:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能不相信外星生命的存在呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you not believe in the existence of extraterrestrial life?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.31,0:28:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有数十亿生命成长的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, there are billions of opportunities for life to grow.
