Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.10,0:28:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是让你一直说"数十亿"的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not to say "billions" a billion times.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.54,0:28:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不可能是宇宙中唯一的星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just... We can't be the only pebble in space
