Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.04,0:29:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这次就免了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got to take a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.02,0:29:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Darby曾经上过一次烹饪课\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darby took a cooking class once.
