Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.35,0:30:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 他真的尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, he really tried. It was sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.85,0:30:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他想学我最爱的菜肴 红酒牛肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wanted to learn my favorite food-- beef bourguignon--
