Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.84,0:30:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来是个好男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.83,0:30:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.59,0:30:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't want it to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.41,0:30:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,和Darby的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With Darby.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.35,0:30:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The divorce was...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.30,0:30:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们唯一的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all we could think to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.39,0:30:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,几周前 我想注册\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couple weeks ago, I tried signing up for an online
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.39,0:30:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在线约会服务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}dating service,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.03,0:30:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但当我填写个人资料的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but when I went to complete the profile, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.49,0:30:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.47,0:30:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为什么 这一步 甚至超过了离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somehow that step--more than the divorce, even--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.41,0:30:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉像是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.42,0:30:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A line you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.52,0:30:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,迈过去就无法回头的线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just can't uncross.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.65,0:30:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get it.
