Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.79,0:31:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一个马夫发现了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of the stable hands found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.60,0:31:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为马钉蹄铁的时候 闻到了这股难闻的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was shoeing a horse, noticed this horrible smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.82,0:31:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是...变质的奶酪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kind of like... spoiled cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.63,0:31:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-经常使用这些马厩么 -几年没用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Use these stables much? - Not in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.78,0:31:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个藏东西的好地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a great place to hide something you don't want found.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.75,0:31:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.21,0:31:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这股味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.43,0:31:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是...变质的奶酪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Definitely... spoiled cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.88,0:31:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好 Loretta\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good afternoon, Loretta.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.94,0:31:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Brody Christopher 来见见Shang Lee\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brody, Christopher, come meet Shang Lee in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.05,0:31:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,腐烂如斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rotting as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.77,0:31:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现他淹没在这个臭水槽里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found him submerged in this trough of fetid water.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.23,0:31:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,死因是胸口的两枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cause of death is two gunshot wounds to the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.15,0:31:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,口径应该是9毫米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Caliber appears to be nine millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.68,0:31:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和杀害Rebecca Ortega的武器一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same weapon that killed Rebecca Ortega.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.64,0:32:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让Sebastian核对弹道 但我猜测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have Sebastian check ballistics, but I'm guessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.96,0:32:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,弹痕会匹配\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Striations match.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.99,0:32:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.27,0:32:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,根据腐烂 肿胀和变色情况判断 我认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Based on decomp, bloating and lividity, I'd say Shang Lee
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.41,0:32:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shang Lee比其他两名受害者要早遇害几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}died hours before the other two victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.79,0:32:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也许该打给Pride\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might want to call Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.18,0:32:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他凶手仍然逍遥法外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him the killer's still on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.33,0:32:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好 就这么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Well, do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.00,0:32:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看来这通电话意味着 危险尚未结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I take it that call doesn't mean the danger's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.73,0:32:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.46,0:32:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.82,0:33:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\i1}So, what happens now?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.18,0:33:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不管凶手是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If... whoever it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.38,0:33:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他能在那么偏僻的地方找到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can find you out here in the middle of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.10,0:33:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们带你回办公室更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's better we bring you back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.96,0:33:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,更安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More security.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.80,0:33:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将对你进行24小时监控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll keep you under 24-hour watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.70,0:33:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.40,0:33:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉之前...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sorry about... before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.97,0:33:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别在意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't give it another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.97,0:33:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我能问你个问题么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.37,0:33:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你那条手链是哪儿来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you get that bracelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.35,0:33:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Darby送的 我30岁生日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darby, my 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.08,0:33:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你的耳环呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your earrings?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.72,0:33:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-也是Darby送的 -都是纯银的么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, Darby, also. - All silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.14,0:33:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我唯一能带的首饰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the only kind of jewelry I can wear
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.86,0:33:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,带别的材质我会起疹子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without breaking into hives.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.48,0:33:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那个盒式吊坠就是银质的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what the locket was made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.96,0:34:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显不是给Rebecca的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It clearly was not for Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.64,0:34:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它和你其它首饰都相配\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It matches everything else you wear, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.51,0:34:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-你觉得他... -他是买给你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You think he... - He bought it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.23,0:34:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也许\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.14,0:34:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它成了藏东西的完美之处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it became the perfect hiding place for something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.14,0:34:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他逃命时携带的唯一东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only thing he took as he ran for his life
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.48,0:34:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那条吊坠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was the necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.13,0:34:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而SD卡可以非常小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And an SD card can be very small.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.44,0:34:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride说再检查一遍盒式吊坠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pride says recheck the locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.17,0:34:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是在现场就检查过了么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought he checked it at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.17,0:34:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,里面什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.12,0:34:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一张SD卡能有多大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How big is an SD card?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.90,0:34:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多像拇指的指甲那么大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can be about the size of your thumbnail.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.89,0:34:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这东西卡住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This thing's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.18,0:34:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-我能试试么 -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- May I? - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.56,0:34:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲总担心丢失她的吊坠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, my mother was always worried about losing her locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.16,0:34:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对于打不开的卡扣 她都是这么办的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is what she would do with a faulty clasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.33,0:35:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mm. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.95,0:35:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看来里面有什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like there's something in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.23,0:35:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐厉害吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you like them apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.70,0:35:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,给我瞧瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me get that, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.65,0:35:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看看这些杀戮究竟是为了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see what all this killing is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好 开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.58,0:35:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这特么是啥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.32,0:35:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, that ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.57,0:35:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.94,0:35:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还有个文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's another file on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.16,0:35:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是个没写完的备忘录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a memo. It's unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.06,0:35:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是Wilson身亡前两天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dated two days before Wilson's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.78,0:35:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要发给海军的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有一封带有Axelord导弹系统视频的邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilson was accidentally cc'd
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.31,0:35:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不小心抄送给了Wilson\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on an e-mail with a video of Axelrod's missile system.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.00,0:35:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,导弹定位系统出了问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a defect with the targeting mechanism,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.91,0:36:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但他在等另一个人的意见 而非立刻向上级报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he's waiting on a second opinion before notifying his superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.58,0:36:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shang Lee可能就是他在等的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shang Lee could have been that second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.18,0:36:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道Axelord如何运作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knew how Axelrod worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.56,0:36:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在铲除一切后患\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're cleaning up all their loose ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.06,0:36:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也因为如此 他们想除掉Katherine\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is probably why they went after Katherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.03,0:36:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她在Wilson死前一天 在家见过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She met with Wilson at his house the day before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.65,0:36:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定是担心 Wilson跟她说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must be scared they told her something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.20,0:36:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 但问题是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but the question is:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.34,0:36:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是Axelrod里的谁 把事情搞砸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who at Axelrod screwed up big-time,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.46,0:36:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,发了那封邮件 然后试图掩盖痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sent that e-mail, and then tried to cover their tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.92,0:36:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我查查看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.77,0:36:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 把设计规格发给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is great. Just send me the specs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.59,0:36:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,NCIS 不许动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}NCIS. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.84,0:36:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoa. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.98,0:36:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.25,0:36:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Schwartz小姐 你得跟我们走一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miss Schwartz, you need to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.32,0:36:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.09,0:36:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jason 我相信一定是哪里出错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason, I'm sure this is a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.85,0:36:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,简直太疯狂了 我不知道你们在想什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is insane. I don't know what you're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.53,0:36:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可以保证 你们抓错人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I can promise you, you have the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.04,0:36:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下再说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold that thought, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.66,0:37:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识他么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You recognize him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.33,0:37:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,允许我帮你恢复一下记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Allow me to refresh your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.69,0:37:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar Randolph 你们公司的安全主管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oscar Randolph, head of security for your company,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.32,0:37:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在意识到Wilson中校无意间接收了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the man you e-mailed ten minutes after you realized
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.72,0:37:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那封导弹测试失败的邮件后十分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Wilson had accidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.88,0:37:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你给Oscar发了邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}received the failed missile test.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.76,0:37:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,前准军事部队 训练有素的杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ex-paramilitary, trained killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.92,0:37:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有使用九毫米手枪和狙击步枪的经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}experience using nine-millimeter and sniper weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.62,0:37:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋码与我们发现的脚印相符\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shoe size matches the prints we found.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.75,0:37:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他干净利索地坦白了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he sings like a canary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.81,0:37:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,比如往中校办公室的胆固醇药片里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About biotrackers in cholesterol meds
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.45,0:37:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,放生物追踪器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}kept at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.58,0:37:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,比如雇凶杀人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}murder for hire,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.20,0:37:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还有如果导弹生意败北\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and lost million-dollar bonuses
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.85,0:37:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就会失去的百万奖金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if a missile deal were to go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.93,0:37:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,交易是这样的 如果你在Pride探员进来前坦白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's the deal.You talk before Agent Pride gets in this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.12,0:37:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会告诉法官宽大处理 如果你保持沉默\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we'll tell the judge to show leniency; you stay silent...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.02,0:37:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就祈祷不会被判死刑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take your chances with the needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.37,0:37:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好好 求求你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.86,0:38:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要知道 我从来没让他去杀Rebecca\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to know, I never told him to kill Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.00,0:38:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她本不该在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wasn't supposed to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.31,0:38:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你会告诉法官这个吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll tell the judge that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.52,0:38:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Randolph先生在那儿 他要找律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Randolph in there-- he...he wants his lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.24,0:38:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他什么也不肯说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.62,0:38:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.48,0:38:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我们的谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep. Conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.71,0:38:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么成效 不过倒是给了我点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}wasn't very fruitful, but it did give me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.16,0:38:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,整理了一下购物清单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}time to put together my grocery list.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.32,0:38:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,需要什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.94,0:38:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Katherine\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Katherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.19,0:38:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在可以回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.32,0:38:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.91,0:38:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不需要担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing else to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.88,0:38:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我得说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got to say, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.79,0:38:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,保护性监禁也有它的好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}protective custody has its advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.53,0:39:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,陪同的伙伴真不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Company wasn't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.56,0:39:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我觉得你可能想要这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. I thought you might like to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.05,0:39:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很好看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.32,0:39:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dardy品味不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darby had good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.22,0:39:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.69,0:40:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在弄这个呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.87,0:40:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 车子很顽固\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Cars can be stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.95,0:40:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,顽固的不只是车子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That ain't the only thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.77,0:40:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想 你为什么还没有修好车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been thinking why you haven't fixed the car yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.98,0:40:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么见解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What'd you come up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.48,0:40:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果车不好使 Linda会一直打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if the car doesn't work, Linda's gonna keep calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.77,0:40:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她就一直存在于的生活中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keeps her in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.85,0:40:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦修好了 就没什么理由打电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once it's fixed, less reason to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.74,0:40:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.40,0:40:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要还给Linda的 我要卖掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not going to Linda. I'm selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.79,0:40:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她收拾了东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, packed her things,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.91,0:40:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,关上家门 去她姐姐家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}closed up the house, went to her sister's.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.85,0:40:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都认为这是最好的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both decided it was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.41,0:40:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样了么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, is this permanent?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.93,0:40:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能不爱这声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you love the sound of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.68,0:40:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,兜个风不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go for a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.30,0:40:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我开车么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna let me drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.14,0:40:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,门儿都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a chance.
